<HEADLINE> National Measurement and Testing Center Set up in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 23 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai Measurement and
Testing Technology Research Institute, a national measurement
inspection body, was established today in the leading industrial
city of China.
</P>
<P>
As one of the two national comprehensive analysis and testing
centers, the institute was founded by the merger of Shanghai Testing
Technology Research Institute and Shanghai Institute of Metrology,
which have sophisticated equipment and technical know-how.
</P>
<P>
The newly established institute will be devoted to research of
measurement and testing technology and analytical testing methods,
the development and manufacturing of measurement devices,
analytical measurement devices, intelligent measurement devices
and sensors.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
