<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Dalian to Host National Hardware Commodity Trade Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DALIAN, October 23 (Xinhua) -- A national commodity hardware
trade fair is to open tomorrow in Dalian, a coastal city in
northeast China's Liaoning Province.
</P>
<P>
The three-day fair is co-sponsored by China Hardware Commercial
Association under the Ministry of Internal Trade, and a local
enterprise group.
</P>
<P>
The fair has attracted more than 10,000 participants from
domestic hardware sectors, and commercial and industrial circles,
as well as some well-knowned manufacturers from foreign countries,
including the United States, Germany, Japan, and the Republic of
Korea.  
</P>
</TEXT>
