<HEADLINE> Greek PM Meets Yugoslav President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, October 23 (Xinhua) -- Greek Prime Minister Costas
Simitis met today with Yugoslav President Zoran Lilic to discuss
bilateral issues with special emphasis on economic cooperation
between the two countries.
</P>
