cooperate with each other on the basis of equality and mutual
benefit as envisaged in the charter should be recognized," it
said.
</P>
<P>
Than Shwe reaffirmed Myanmar's confidence in the UN charter and
commitment to lasting world peace and security, international law
and order, and international cooperation for accelerated
development in developing countries.  
