development of relations between Russia and Ukraine.
</P>
<P>
Yastrzhembsky said Yeltsin and Kuchma had agreed that Russian
Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin would visit Kiev in November to
sign a package of agreements on the fleet's division, and on
relevant financial issues.
</P>
