cooperation between Iran and Italy, as well as the regional
developments such as the crisis in Afghanistan, northern Iraq,
Tajikistan, the Middle East and the Gulf region.
</P>
<P>
Describing the talks as positive, the Iranian official said
that the two sides placed emphasis on continuation of regular
bilateral talks on various regional and international issues.
</P>
<P>
In response, Toia stressed the implementation of the
memorandum of understanding and assured that her country will
precisely follow up the provisions of the agreement. 
