<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Ranked Best Place for Shopping, Eating </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 24 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong has been ranked the
most popular Asian destination for shopping and eating, according
to a consumer survey conducted by MasterCard International.
</P>
<P>
One out of every three Asians rated Hong Kong as the best spot
for shopping, and Singapore came to be the second best choice,
says the survey.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong also won the most votes as the paradise of gourmets
for variety and quality of food, followed by Thailand and
Singapore.
</P>
<P>
Conductors of the survey interviewed about 400 high and
medium-income people in each of 12 countries and regions in the
Asia-Pacific region.
</P>
<P>
The survey was aimed at capturing a snapshot of consumer
preference and spending habits in the region so as to help the
credit-card companies and member banks to gain a better
understanding of their clients, according to MasterCard
International.  
