arrived in Damascus Monday afternoon. Shortly after arrival,
Fischer and members of the delegation held talks with Kaddura, in
which the Syrian speaker stressed his country's insistence on a
fair and overall peace based on the relevant U.N. resolutions and
the land-for-peace principle.
</P>
<P>
In response, Fischer said that all parties concerned
should seek to achieve a just and comprehensive peace in the
Middle East. 
</P>
