development of the two former Soviet republics' relations.
</P>
<P>
The source said that Kuchma would begin his talks with Yeltsin
in the Barvikha sanatorium near Moscow immediately after his
arrival. The Ukrainian leader is also expected to meet with
Russian Prime Minister Viktor Chernomyrdin later today. 
