a year-on-year basis, reaching 4,567.5 billion yuan (550.3 billion
US dollars).
</P>
<P>
-- China is opening a new channel for introducing foreign
investment in its water supply projects, using a development
method known as "build, operate and transfer" (BOT).
</P>
<P>
Under the BOT method, projects are built by foreign private
capital and then transferred to China after several years of
operation. 
