<HEADLINE> Gore Criticizes Dole Tax Plan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, October 23 (Xinhua) -- Referring to the 1980s
recession, Vice President Al Gore blamed Republicans on Wednesday
for past economic problems.
</P>
